{"tid":2303811,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：新高中課程通識科加入內地考察   (我的兒子在澳洲讀書)","createTime":"2020-11-28T09:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T09:21:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f95cc7408af50fb315775c10bff8cfae96971ec0","tid":2303811,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:00:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562452-20201127.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562452-20201127.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7Cns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=56c0d9e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562452-20201127.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=651f5a71\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562452-20201127.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄表示，新高中課程通識科加入內地考察，並不計入公開試評分，當局不能迫學生到內地。<br />\n<br />\n他提到政府的決定與檢討專責小組有不同屬正常，任何教育改革都會對教師有影響，當局會協助他們轉型，包括轉教其他科目。<br />\n<br />\n教育界立法會議員葉建源表示，政府未有按程序讓課程發展議會討論改動，要求教育局提供理據，如未能提供，便反映這是隨便的政治決定，將社會混亂的責任推卸予給通識教育科，形容通識教育是「代罪羔羊」。"},{"pid":"258540643fccf8c3cd536be5e304b273b08454ad","tid":2303811,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:01:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"771a6e8219d8e5fa0012cab127a9a3d47ba8941a","tid":2303811,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2175000/2178009/study_thumb_20181008_S_V2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2175000%2F2178009%2Fstudy_thumb_20181008_S_V2_600.jpg&h=7366a5c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181007/s00001/070c8564f0a2aa23663e4096436dd916.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2